  "title": "“中国云谷”高校训练营暨 ROS 春季学校首期圆满收官！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk3NTc1NTU0Mw==&mid=2247507225&idx=2&sn=547e5ff16b4ebf6344258f8e49f71d6c",
