  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span>魔搭ModelScope社区</span> <span>2026-04-09 20:51</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">浙江</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c4ba92d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fia2awwZLWFZTyu1cbnt2XO4sR6yVVkcx8Ones9LoQRwgm6tXSFDLsrkibJsJZXRChCMrNyh9Aq2XUaHwXOHThibTrIb5ewFVdTmn4NiaALXpiagw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>2026年4月6日，“中国云谷”高校训练营暨ROS春季学校首期在杭州云谷中心结业，活动汇聚百名学子，引入机器狗及人形机器人进行具身智能实战教学，旨在推进AI科产教融合。</p>\n  <div data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"KM7qeobmBDBJblpj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">4月6日，随着训练营结业仪式圆满结束，为期三天的“中国云谷”高校训练营暨ROS春季学校在云谷中心正式落下帷幕。本次活动由机器人操作系统（ROS）教育基金会主办，萝卜园具身智能生态社区、云谷中心、魔搭社区承办，汇聚云深处科技、智元机器人、智谷未来等企业力量，聚焦具身智能主题，为来自全国的100名高校学子打造了一场集“工业级平台+真实场景+系统级工程”于一体的沉浸式学习体验。本次训练营见证了学生们对具身智能的学习热情，也感受到“从课堂到产业”这条人才培养新路径正在一步步走深走实。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100023540\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" style=\"width: 800px;height: 533.5px;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d5b7ab5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fia2awwZLWFZR3UUJ1lP7zFVQoYibXU5tbXkob4ibya8p1HltBgAxzuMPR3pfNpFtZQx0hicyFjXFaRYdgTJxCl7G31Sl0wzRgxBBMUQ6b5U3SpM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"KM7qeobmBDBJblpj\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">亲手“操练”机器狗与人形机器人，告别具身智能“纸上谈兵”</span></span></span></h3>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">此次训练营引入云深处科技的四足机器人（机器狗）和智元机器人的灵犀X2双足机器人（人形机器人）等平台，让平时难以接触高端实体机器人的高校学生，亲手体验操作、调试设备的感受。在课程设计上，训练营设置了“四足机器人系统实训”与“人形机器人系统实训”两大模块。从传统运动控制到强化学习实操，从ROS2系统搭建到二次开发实践，全部基于行业真实工程任务。学员们在导师指导下，完成了现场导师设置的各项场景化考核，真正实现了从“算法设计”到“实体机器人运行”的全流程跨越。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"91330\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;\">\n     <div data-role=\"animate\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\">\n      <div data-divisor=\"1\" style=\"overflow: hidden;width: 200%;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 200% !important;\" data-width=\"200%\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669106881405563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-imgfileid=\"100023544\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dda22c52&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fia2awwZLWFZQzia44fpowiaWMblrQmU0QRgiavP4qQE1dojM0Dq9WC7V9vXHoMOic3JFTbicl4fSl3lId1jfiaYRicSljcbm9icmgh9pFSC9N3od1SBA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669316375198728\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1258\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-imgfileid=\"100023543\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=467b9923&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fia2awwZLWFZSvHZX3dHQbZaTRkZMFpu0Xflcib8oRAmxC1Uib12G7pwv0l7S1335FXFK7rFWBC31wnweP0iaOA3kGyUVicJK3edwhfAA83icEiaxf4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"line-height:32px;margin: 10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看更多</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">云深处科技、智元机器人、智谷未来等企业专家授课，3天掌握具身智能实战技能</span></span></span></h3>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本次训练营采用“小班制+导师制”，由云深处科技、智元机器人、智谷未来等企业的技术专家全程授课。在四足机器人课程中，学员们从基础操作入手，逐步掌握二次开发接口使用，强化学习模型部署、感知系统调试等核心技能；在双足机器人课程中，学员们从机器人操作系统（ROS）入手，重点学习了机器人操作系统的结构与运作逻辑，并且结合大模型进行基于仿真系统的实践；随后，学员们围绕灵犀X2的架构解析、二次开发接口使用、运动控制与感知决策协同等内容展开实践，最终通过小组协作完成复杂任务。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这种“动手+实用”的实战模式，让学员们在短短三天内，不仅掌握了ROS2系统开发的核心技能，更建立了团队协作与工程思维。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"91330\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;\">\n     <div data-role=\"animate\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\">\n      <div data-divisor=\"1\" style=\"overflow: hidden;width: 200%;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 200% !important;\" data-width=\"200%\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669106881405563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-imgfileid=\"100023545\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=96259512&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fia2awwZLWFZQaiclJzmCPJ9E7ArDYy7fdichYWjDHeSjxXLhInbpPdD1qXCnicNkromTYtzXhBq2XTGbJS70UdYF5CzgwVCy9bIR6n7ToAmZxjk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669106881405563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-imgfileid=\"100023546\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d497b435&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fia2awwZLWFZQ5aOZ2NRsEa8VFH7SibyT5NDyHKbHkRJZ0LKhlu5I2TzTBq0zwMGeMJCwNRibUzbmjaohtmUt1JYjPicz2LThr15Dz0sn0FY6uDs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"line-height:32px;margin: 10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看更多</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-weight: bold;\">结业不落幕，“中国云谷”高校训练营将继续交出科产教融合新答卷</span></span></span></h3>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">训练营结业仪式上，杭州紫金港科技城管理委员会党工委副书记、主任徐东旭和机器人操作系统（ROS）教育基金会主席张新宇教授为本次训练营的学生授予结业证书。西湖大学赵世钰教授、杭州云深处科技教育行业副总监徐刘玉、智元机器人技术生态专家韩俊带来的行业前沿报告，让学员们真切感受到了产业发展的强劲脉搏。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这不仅是一次技能集训，更是一次技术、产业与人才的深度对接，从课堂到产业，从技术到生态——“中国云谷”高校训练营，正在为AI未来蓄力。期待更多AI新生力量的加入，共筑AI产业生态。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"91330\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div style=\"margin: 10px auto;\">\n     <div data-role=\"animate\" style=\"display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;overflow-x: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\">\n      <div data-divisor=\"1\" style=\"overflow: hidden;width: 200%;display: flex;flex-flow: row;box-sizing: border-box;max-width: 200% !important;\" data-width=\"200%\">\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669106881405563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-imgfileid=\"100023548\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ada26a8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fia2awwZLWFZTVicaU6NBticOwySQFbaE57bEp5urHKhRjp02EbQFJm4TQaEibANBBjrsD2DdjSVuZWa5EmkGsMMtWannu7KwJyy4c3dI3T60qBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;width: 50%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-width=\"50%\">\n        <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: 0;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <p style=\"vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;max-width: 100% !important;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-width=\"100%\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6669106881405563\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" style=\"vertical-align:baseline;\" data-imgfileid=\"100023547\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5611b79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fia2awwZLWFZRF9ibmic1ibsdyeiaWZpE4KmjOOkxXdsQF3R0XkbKCKSsEoSqC5XEnhmBB1doRD22gxbMWhGXx9TriaiaRrOBdwPB4w8F7tRRO6m9J8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <div>\n      <p style=\"line-height:32px;margin: 10px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">左右滑动查看更多</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“中国云谷”高校训练营</span></span></span><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.6;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">是云谷中心和紫金港科技城共同打造的 AI 科产教融合发展标杆项目，链接高校学生、产业生态、政策扶持，构建“技术学习—场景认知—产业对接”的产业联动机制，推进人才链、产业链、创新链深度融合，为 AI 生态引育未来力量。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span data-type=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"colo